---
title: Italian Lamb Ragu Fettuccine Feast with Garlic Bread & Cucumber Salad
description: It’s pasta night! This sumptuous yet simple dish is absolute decadence in a bowl. Rich and indulgent ragu wraps around tendrils of fettuccine for a truly epic combination. Sprinkle some Parmesan on top, and don’t be too surprised if the bowls are left licked clean.
